arceration -- Home.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1335\u13\'0d\u13\'0dLet me not mar that perfect Dream By an Auroral stain But so adjust my daily Night That it will come again.\u13\'0d\u13\'0dNot when we know, the Power accosts -- The Garment of Surprise Was all our timid Mother wore At Home -- in Paradise.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1336\u13\'0d\u13\'0dNature assigns the Sun -- That -- is Astronomy -- Nature cannot enact a Friend -- That -- is Astrology.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1337\u13\'0d\u13\'0dUpon a Lilac Sea To toss incessantly His Plush Alarm Who fleeing from the Spring The Spring avenging fling To Dooms of Balm\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1338\u13\'0d\u13\'0dWhat tenements of clover Are fitting for the bee, What edifices azure For butterflies and me -- What residences nimble Arise and evanesce Without a rhythmic rumor Or an assaulting guess.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1339\u13\'0d\u13\'0dA Bee his burnished Carriage Drove boldly to a Rose -- Combinedly alighting -- Himself -- his Carriage was -- The Rose received his visit With frank tranquillity Withholding not a Crescent To his Cupidity -- Their Moment consummated -- Remained for him -- to flee -- Remained for her -- of rapture But the humility.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1340\u13\'0d\u13\'0dA Rat surrendered here A brief career of Cheer And Fraud and Fear.\u13\'0d\u13\'0dOf Ignominy's due Let all addicted to Beware.\u13\'0d\u13\'0dThe most obliging Trap Its tendency to snap Cannot resist --\u13\'0d\u13\'0dTemptation is the Friend Repugnantly resigned At last.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1341\u13\'0d\u13\'0dUnto the Whole -- how add? Has "All" a further realm -- Or Utmost an Ulterior? Oh, Subsidy of Balm!\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1342\u13\'0d\u13\'0d"Was not" was all the Statement. The Unpretension stuns -- Perhaps -- the Comprehension -- They wore no Lexicons -\u13\'0d\u13\'0dBut lest our Speculation In inanition die Because "God took him" mention -- That was Philology --\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1343\u13\'0d\u13\'0dA single Clover Plank Was all that saved a Bee A Bee I personally knew From sinking in the sky --\u13\'0d\u13\'0d'Twixt Firmament above\u13\'0d\u13\'0dAnd Firmament below The Billows of Circumference Were sweeping him away --\u13\'0d\u13\'0dThe idly swaying Plank Responsible to nought A sudden Freight of Wind assumed And Bumble Bee was not --\u13\'0d\u13\'0dThis harrowing event Transpiring in the Grass Did not so much as wring from him A wandering "Alas" --\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1344\u13\'0d\u13\'0dNot any more to be lacked -- Not any more to be known -- Denizen of Significance For a span so worn --\u13\'0d\u13\'0dEven Nature herself Has forgot it is there -- Sedulous of her Multitudes Notwithstanding Despair --\u13\'0d\u13\'0dOf the Ones that pursued it Suing it not to go Some have solaced the longing To accompany --\u13\'0d\u13\'0dSome -- rescinded the Wrench -- Others -- Shall I say Plated the residue of Adz With Monotony.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1345\u13\'0d\u13\'0dAn antiquated Grace Becomes that cherished Face As well as prime Enjoining us to part We and our pouting Heart Good friends with time 1346\u13\'0d\u13\'0dAs Summer into Autumn slips And yet we sooner say "The Summer" than "the Autumn," lest We turn the sun away,\u13\'0d\u13\'0dAnd almost count it an Affront The presence to concede Of one however lovely, not The one that we have loved --\u13\'0d\u13\'0dSo we evade the charge of Years On one attempting shy The Circumvention of the Shaft Of Life's Declivity.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1347\u13\'0d\u13\'0dEscape is such a thankful Word I often in the Night Consider it unto myself No spectacle in sight\u13\'0d\u13\'0dEscape -- it is the Basket In which the Heart is caught When down some awful Battlement The rest of Life is dropt --\u13\'0d\u13\'0d'Tis not to sight the savior -- It is to be the saved -- And that is why I lay my Head Upon this trusty word --\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1348\u13\'0d\u13\'0dLift it -- with the Feathers Not alone we fly -- Launch it -- the aquatic Not the only sea -- Advocate the Azure To the lower Eyes -- He has obligation Who has Paradise --\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1349\u13\'0d\u13\'0dI'd rather recollect a setting Than own a rising sun Though one is beautiful forgetting -And true the other one.\u13\'0d\u13\'0dBecause in going is a Drama Staying cannot confer To die divinely once a Twilight -- Than wane is easier --\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1350\u13\'0d\u13\'0dLuck is not chance -- It's Toil -- Fortune's expensive smile Is earned - The Father of the Mine Is that old-fashioned Coin We spurned --\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1351\u13\'0d\u13\'0dYou cannot take itself From any Human soul -- That indestructible estate Enable him to dwell -- Impregnable as Light That every man behold But take away as difficult As undiscovered Gold --\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1352\u13\'0d\u13\'0dTo his simplicity To die -- was little Fate -If Duty live -- contented But her Confederate.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1353\u13\'0d\u13\'0dThe last of Summer is Delight -- Deterred by Retrospect. 'Tis Ecstasy's revealed Review -- Enchantment's Syndicate.\u13\'0d\u13\'0dTo meet it -- nameless as it is -- Without celestial Mail - Audacious as without a Knock To walk within the Veil.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1354\u13\'0d\u13\'0dThe Heart is the Capital of the Mind -- The Mind is a single State -- The Heart and the Mind together make A single Continent --\u13\'0d\u13\'0dOne -- is the Population -- Numerous enough -- This ecstatic Nation Seek -- it is Yourself.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1355 The Mind lives on the Heart Like any Parasite -- If that is full of Meat The Mind is fat.\u13\'0d\u13\'0dBut if the Heart omit Emaciate the Wit -- The Aliment of it So absolute.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1356\u13\'0d\u13\'0dThe Rat is the concisest Tenant. He pays no Rent. Repudiates the Obligation -- On Schemes intent\u13\'0d\u13\'0dBalking our Wit To sound or circumvent -- Hate cannot harm A Foe so reticent -- Neither Decree prohibit him -- Lawful as Equilibrium.\u13\'0d\u13\'0d1357\u13\'0d\u13\'0d"Faithful to the end" Amended From the Heavenly Clause -- Constancy with a Proviso Constancy abhors --\u13\'0d\u13\'0d"Crowns of Life" are servile Prizes 